{
  "text": "In the previous section we considered the system given by (6) for real values of the deformation parameter. But it may be very interesting also in the case when the deformation parameter q is a root of unity. The reason is that in that case we can also define finite-dimensional representations. Note that this case is not related to the bosonic relations [CITATION_1] .",
